      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAST COMMAND (5) got the job done over this track and trip last time out and winning rider McMurray sticks in the stirrups. Again gets the benefit of his 2kg claim and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. MR BUSTER (4) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Tuned up for this with a recent trial and can run a big race while fresh. FREE CARRY (6) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim. Top-three candidate. WEIGALL TIGER (1) has a solid record around this circuit and will be ready to peak now third-up from the break. In the mix on best figures. CANBERRA LEGEND (7) best of the rest from the inside marble.",
